{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "雖非同族", "storyInfo": "從自救軍成員洛洛口中，阿米婭得知疑似特蕾西婭的白髮薩卡茲的消息。地面上，號角發覺深池士兵的異動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "3:22 P.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆，薩迪恩區，地下結構"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不覺得這是個明智的選擇。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛，我們人手不夠。上面我們還沒查過的能藏人的地方還有多少？至少占薩迪恩區的三分之一。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，哈默哥他們已經在準備轉移工作，等過了這兩天，指揮官他們就會離開這裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，就算我們小隊留下搜尋，成功機率也會小得多。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並不能構成你想讓那些人加入我們的理由。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是加入......是互相幫助。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是聽到指揮官的話了嗎？他們是朋友的朋友。我們答應了那位朋友的請求，幫他們進入倫蒂尼姆，而他們已經來到這裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，要是他們能幫我們找人的話......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們可以在我們的據點休整。這是指揮官的命令。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等他們休息好了，他們就會離開這裡。我會護送他們到地面上安全的地方，可也到此為止了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼不能問問他們願不願意暫時留下？只是一個小忙而已，他們未必會拒絕。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道為什麼，我說過了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官認為他們值得信任，這一定是有理由的。所以我不會再質疑他們的身份和動機。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我不想讓我們的人攪和進無關的危險裡。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得他們要做的事很危險？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為他們是來幹什麼的？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶著一隊身懷絕技的薩卡茲潛入倫蒂尼姆，把另一撥薩卡茲當作敵人......費斯特，我們是維多利亞人，應當見慣了這種事。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是說那些天天在倫蒂尼姆外面打架的貴族老爺。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自我們出生起，他們就打得沒完沒了，不是嗎？要不是他們只顧著自己打架，我們的家也不會成了薩卡茲的別院。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們光是要把自己的家搶回來，就已經夠累了......薩卡茲們想在我們的土地上打起來，我們根本無力阻止，更何況這與我們也無關。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......萬一他們真的能阻止城內的薩卡茲呢？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你覺得他們只是為了搶另一頂王冠，但至少目前看來，我們有著共同的敵人。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特，我沒你那麼自信，總以為我們能掌控局面。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲......薩卡茲根本就不是你想的那樣，他們很會偽裝。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸被處死的那天，我遠遠地看見了一個人......那些劊子手叫她殿下。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那個時候，我才知道，原來統率群魔的王，竟然是那副模樣。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你從來沒有跟我說起過這件事。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為那時候我以為沒這個必要。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我要告訴你......我希望你知道，我們不能被表象蒙蔽。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使那位薩卡茲女性有著純白無瑕的外貌，即使她會為一個無關緊要的倫蒂尼姆老工人露出那般悲傷的神情，我都不會忘記......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是她帶領著那些薩卡茲殺死了我爸爸，也殺死了無數維多利亞人......她是魔王！", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#3$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......阿米婭小姐？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#2$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費斯特先生，洛洛小姐......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我說完了，隊長。我回地面繼續我們的搜查任務，你......請你考慮一下我的話。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭小姐，博士，抱歉......那個，我要幫哈默哥調整裝備......我也先離開一下。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_402_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，洛洛小姐說的那位薩卡茲......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "還沒有足夠的資訊。;......;聽起來不是很像特雷西斯。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line93", "option2": "line93", "option3": "line93"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一位......有著悲憫神情的白髮女性。其他薩卡茲叫她殿下。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，雖然你忘記了，但是我......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忘不了她的每一個最細微的表情，還有她對我說的每一句話。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你的意思是......;......;怎麼可能！", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line101", "option2": "line101", "option3": "line101"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很清楚，這不可能。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_bridge", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Dr.{@nickname}，從今天開始，你將擁有調取以下檔案的權限。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會在這些檔案裡找到一部分你關心的資訊——", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是關於她，還是關於阿米婭目前所繼承的那部分力量。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我記得你說過，你不信我。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line118"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這個時間點上，談論信任與否已經沒有意義。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我無法否認你對阿米婭而言的重要性。此次倫蒂尼姆行動，她最需要的就是你的幫助。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論你們在倫蒂尼姆看見什麼，請和阿米婭一起面對。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你能做到。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，別著急。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line136"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊......我不應該著急。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我差一點就想去追洛洛小姐，問清楚她看見的到底是誰。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的話......可能會加深她對我們的誤解。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭也可以有自己的情緒。;阿米婭對自己已經很嚴格了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line145", "option2": "line145"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......博士，我好些了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在來倫蒂尼姆之前，你應該已經從凱爾希醫生口中瞭解到了一些過去的事......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但有些話，我還沒有機會說。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實，在那件事之後，有很長一段時間，我都會夢見你們。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我的夢裡，你從來沒有開過口，你只是安靜地守著我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像過去那些荒地上的夜晚一樣，你沉默地握著我的手，因為只有這樣，我才能放心睡著。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感覺到你......那時候，我知道你只是睡著了，Dr.{@nickname}，你也許暫時不在我的身邊，但你依然陪伴著我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭......", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line159"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是她......不一樣。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在夢裡對我說了很多話，從羅德島上每一個薩卡茲的命運，到我那一天是不是睡不好，有沒有著涼......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她叮囑了我許多事，就彷彿她還在我身邊似的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越是這樣......越是這樣，我就越清楚地感覺到，她已經離開我們了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "相信你的感覺。;......;你是最清楚的人。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line169", "option2": "line169", "option3": "line169"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她很不捨......非常非常不捨。她心裡記掛的人和事本來就有那麼多。我們，凱爾希醫生，羅德島，薩卡茲......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果......她真的還在，她怎麼可能不回來？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你們口中的那個人，不會做這種事。;肯定只是一場誤會。;會不會是特雷西斯做了什麼？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line176", "option2": "line181", "option3": "line185"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line192"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，她絕不可能拋下我們不管。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#15$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且她不會縱容特雷西斯入侵維多利亞......她無法忍受薩卡茲挑起這樣一場不義的戰爭。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#17$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line192"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士的意思是，洛洛小姐看到的是另一位與她相似的薩卡茲？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確有這個可能性。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line192"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種手段......非常殘忍。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲比任何種族都要重視死亡。死去的薩卡茲的精魂會回歸整個族群，這是對薩卡茲一生苦難的最好慰藉。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你也見證了愛國者先生的逝去。那關乎尊嚴、榮譽，和一個人一生最後一次對自身命運的詰問。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而死亡的寧靜會給出一個答案，這個答案將包容他的一切。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任何薩卡茲都不該被剝奪這最後的平靜......尤其是她，她已然為薩卡茲奉獻了全部。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你還記不記得我在出入口岸說的話？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道盤踞在倫蒂尼姆中心的情感是什麼了。那是憤怒，薩卡茲的憤怒。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不光我能聽見，這憤怒已經強烈到了每一個薩卡茲都能聽到的地步。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是溫迪戈的祭壇也無法起到這麼強烈的共鳴效果。就好像，有人把薩卡茲燒了成千上萬年的怨恨凝聚成了一團實體的火焰......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒人阻止的話，它早晚會焚穿倫蒂尼姆的天幕，然後蔓延開去，燒盡萬千生靈。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我們需要儘早靠近它，確認引燃一切的焰心是什麼。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我擔心你，阿米婭。;靠近它，你會不會受傷？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line207", "option2": "line207"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你看出來了。是的，我的心態......和以前不完全一樣。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急著奔向那團火焰的人並不是羅德島的負責人，可能也不是他們口中的繼承人......而是阿米婭。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的渴望，是我這個個體想要的答案。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......我確實有一點害怕。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，我害怕那個答案，我不想看到凱爾希醫生和大家心碎......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "還有你自己，阿米婭。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line218"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，是的，還有我自己。假如那真的是她......我不願意想像......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我必須面對，我沒有其他路可以選。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我和你一起面對。;我們一起把路走出來。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line225", "option2": "line225"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，博士......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅僅只是感覺到你在身邊，我就有了走下去的勇氣。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#8$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這就去找克洛維希婭指揮官，提出合作方案。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們需要更多人手來救出被薩卡茲關押的戰友。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也需要他們的幫助。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照原定計劃，我們本該已經見到我們的接應人，也就是那位信使女士。我們必須確認她的安危。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是自救軍的朋友，或許指揮官能幫我們找到她。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，接下來進入中央城區的路途，如果能有他們指引，肯定也會更加順利。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島會向倫蒂尼姆市民自救軍證明，我們絕不是為了薩卡茲的王冠而來。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，深池士兵的動向非常奇怪！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他們正在往某一個方向轉移。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那塊區域不是被薩卡茲重兵把守著嗎？以前深池都不敢靠近那裡的！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們一定有理由。我最好跟上去。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這會不會有點冒險......他們的人數是我們的十倍。", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我一個人去。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們繼續按原定計劃，去他們的據點找東西。他們才剛開始移動，物資應該還沒來得及帶走。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......注意安全。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是！", "name": "羅本"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_413_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，抓緊了。長官一秒都不想耽擱！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我知道你不情願。誰情願做這個？那幫魔族佬，竟敢把我們當雇傭兵一樣差遣！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但別讓我看見你偷懶。在薩卡茲面前，我們誰都別丟長官的臉。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你怎麼還不跟上來？M-611，回話！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼回事？", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......是你！M-601，呼叫......呃啊！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也別出聲。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔呃......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊器拿過來。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_unlock", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你可以說話了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，你們要替薩卡茲做什麼？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我怎麼可能跟你說這些......維多利亞的惡狼......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我想想，深池是怎麼對付那些不願意開口的維多利亞士兵的？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......吊在十幾米高的滑輪裝置上，對吧？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜，我不會什麼變出石柱的源石技藝，做不到輕輕鬆鬆地把人送到那麼高的地方。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你不會用這種手段......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也對，要是我像你們的長官那樣無恥，我也不至於會眼睜睜看著自己的隊員一個個地犧牲在小丘郡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那這樣吧。我綁起你的手腳，然後把你丟到隨便哪個廢棄工廠裡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的工廠在附近有很多，一個個去找的話，大概也花不了多少時間。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才是我的做法，沒錯吧？我就是靠這樣的耐心，從你們手裡找到了一些可憐的士兵。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你在黑暗中絕望地餓死之前，你的長官也能找到你......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......不！長官她不會......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "饒了我吧，你想知道什麼？我只是聽命行事，很多事情我也不明白......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想也是。那名薩卡茲的指揮官可比你的指揮官聰明多了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他心裡到底有什麼計劃，蔓德拉不可能猜得到。你們只能這樣被薩卡茲們耍得團團轉......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行吧，你只需要告訴我你們的目的地。剩下的事情，我自己去弄清楚。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g4_giantwall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然回來了，你還不如早些來見我。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰叫你的客人這麼多嘛。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忘了，你不想見赦罪師的信使。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一讓他發現我在你這裡，那我偷懶的日子豈不是到頭了？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你也不必等到赫德雷走了以後才現身。他是我的人，不會對王庭透露你的行蹤。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，你的人？你別騙自己了，你壓根誰都不信。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是你真信他，你直接喊我出來不行嗎？是你等到那個深池的菲林和你的雇傭兵朋友都走了以後，才和我打招呼的啊。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不說這些。今天早上，你幫我把深池的人引到了約好的位置，我會記得這份人情。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......這只是一件小事。而且，我還有一些意外的收獲哦。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......意外收獲？能讓你這麼說，肯定不是發現了區區幾個反抗軍。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼......你在下面還見到了羅德島的人？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不止哦。不是我見到了他們，而是他們把我從深池士兵的手裡“救”了下來，我們一起到了城牆外。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，要不是你急著試驗你這些寶貝武器，害得我不得不被“炸死”在他們面前，說不定我還能繼續跟著他們。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，我還想和她再好好聊一聊的。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我說，還有機會呢？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又要請我幫忙？你不是讓深池和雇傭兵一起去守臨時監獄了嗎？我以為你都做足了準備，只差請君入甕了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從不會嫌保險太多。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧好吧，那你又欠我們一份人情了。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我是不是說了“我們”？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒關係，除了我，不會有人聽見。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我們真不太想再留在這裡......那個自戀的到哪都要端著高腳杯的老傢伙也快到了，不是嗎？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也千萬別告訴他我們在這裡。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。我會記住閣下的好意。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#7$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......閣下最好不要再頂著死者的面貌繼續行動了。即便不說容易暴露的問題，這也讓我......有些不適。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#8$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，我們都忘了，你可真是個有道德的好薩卡茲，對吧，特雷西斯的學徒？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，下次來見你的，絕對不會再是“托馬斯先生”。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}